<br>
Wake up call...  it does not.  This item is nothing better then fire resist gear.  And since a crown of froglok kings has 12 ac, and 20 fire and cold this item is rated up there in the 50 PP range.<br>
<br>
I don't mean to degrade the seller.  What I am trying to get across is the fact that enchanters still *think* they are better able to mez with higher cha.<br>
<br>
Mez = your lvl vs mob lvl + mr<br>
Charm = your lvl + cha( effects duration ) vs Mob lvl + mr<br>
<br>
Enchanters that waste time casting adoring grace and have 1600 hps because they the are loaded down with cha gear to get 255 are about as useful as a 2 dollar whore.  Sure they get the rocks off with crack and speed, but over all it's not a fun filled night of long enduring sex.<br>
<br>
If you want proof... reserch it yourself.  This is not a flame in any way.  Just something I wish more enchanters were aware of.<br>
